== Ball grid array == {{main article|Ball grid array}}
Ball Grid Array [[Ball grid array|BGA]] uses the underside of the package to place pads with [[balls of solder]] in grid pattern as connections to PCB.<ref name=cpushack/><ref name=interfacebusSOIC/>
